sentences: Selma George is an Indian film singer in Malayalam cinema during the 1970s.
She sang in 40 films, and her most popular song was "Saradindu Malardeepa" from the 1979 film, Ulkadal.
She married Malayalam film director K. G. George on 7 February 1977, at the St. Mathias Church in Chennai.
